{"tid":1453888,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"制裁香港政府集中討論（一）財政預算","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:08:49.000Z","uid":282435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b01f87725f4a2e60569926266b79a9bf831203d6","tid":1453888,"uid":282435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2KeczS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2KeczS.png&h=efb9833e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n薪俸稅<br />\n利得稅<br />\n<br />\n集中討論方法"},{"pid":"714bee0b3230a16c44c6f4eb29c98ee57599f2f2","tid":1453888,"uid":282435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"我先！<br />\n<br />\n薪俸稅中，有一環係可以叫公司將你本來人工的一半變成租津。 租津會以10% 來計稅。<br />\n<br />\n比如本來3皮，變成萬五人工，萬五租津！<br />\n咁你既 assessable income 就變成15000+ 1500<br />\n<br />\n加上本來啲免稅額，呢到已經交少一大截！<br />\n<br />\n要提意公司幫你搞的，但一般醒少少既中級管理人員可以掌握相關稅務條款。唔難的！"},{"pid":"8e054b16eb45ffac6a1451f5af23b328d4d73482","tid":1453888,"uid":282435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:47:08.000Z","msg":"（二）罷買係唔夠的<br />\n<br />\n一定要連自由行既Luxury product 去減。佢少賣隻錶，等於你唔食半年飯。<br />\n<br />\n所以要用不合作運動，主要係單價、單客、單店的高額零售。方法地點大家可以自己諗。<br />\n<br />\n大部分公司，如果做100蚊生意，賺到10蚊已經好好。Net income/ Sales 10%。 所以目標只要減到10%，佢地要交既利得稅就會少好多。"},{"pid":"1f489c15dca58970fbf812621ab041bf5ac52501","tid":1453888,"uid":282435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:47:30.000Z","msg":"無人回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c4e8af36877556cbec5bee6a0544a6f4adfe66","tid":1453888,"uid":282435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:59:23.000Z","msg":"係咪我呢個方向真係咁無用"},{"pid":"32e6687a01d1eb355f6bce4b5936f72635f8eead","tid":1453888,"uid":282435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:59:34.000Z","msg":"完全無人回"},{"pid":"a084131954f15e192ba36238355646f0271580be","tid